---
title: Gochujang Turkey Mince Udon with baby corn and coriander
description: These spicy noodles are fragrant and delicious. Baby corn adds a wonderful crunch, while the coriander garnish adds a freshness that's pleasing to the palette.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W36_IE_IEXCP25295-2_MAIN__high-33939974.jpg
